    "description": "We at Berger Silk Store Advisory Limited are looking for an experienced Assistant Store Manager based out of Agra. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Berger Silk Store Advisory Limited:\nBerger Silk Store Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Agra, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Berger Silk Store Advisory Limited!",
